Infrastructure automation improves consistency, reduces manual errors, and accelerates deployments.

Recommended practices include:

* Automate repetitive deployments
* Maintain infrastructure as code
* Use version control
* Validate deployments before production
* Standardize resource configurations

For example, a development team can deploy identical testing environments repeatedly without manual configuration.

A real-life use case is enterprises provisioning hundreds of virtual machines with consistent security settings.

Automation improves operational efficiency while ensuring repeatable and reliable deployments.
